name: cosmica #1
description: comsica by CSA & digital-art-revolution-berlin is a series of 5 digital transcripts of colour experiments, which the artist has been performing over decades. this is the 1st time the artists work appears digital, in nft-format on hit et nunc. there will be altogether only 5 different pieces (5/5) for an entry price of 1-5 xtz. for more info pls contact curator @AWahllos via twitter.
